  <num>4-754.51</num>
  <heading>Establishment of Office of Shelter Monitoring.</heading>
  <text>There is established within the Department of Human Services an Office of Shelter Monitoring to monitor shelters and services provided by the District and its contractors to clients who are homeless.</text>
  <annotations>
    <annotation doc="D.C. Law 16-35" type="History" path="§27a">Oct. 22, 2005, D.C. Law 16-35, § 27a</annotation>
